        <mxCell id="features_box" value="Key features (added in lab):&#10;• N extracted from prompt (5 most cited → N=5)&#10;• arXiv ID + DOI normalised for grounding check&#10;• S2 batch enrichment for real citation ranking&#10;• Markdown-escape + line-aware split + retry without parse_mode&#10;• Rate-limit aware retries; agent bails to user-friendly message&#10;  instead of looping 8× when both APIs throttle&#10;• Token + USD cost tracked per run via callbacks" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFFFFF;strokeColor=#666666;align=left;fontSize=10;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=10;spacingTop=8;" vertex="1" parent="1">
